BTTTriggers.BTTPredefinedActionName: Open URL / Open URL With Selection

BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString: set json to do shell script "curl -H 'CB-VERSION: 2015-04-08' https://api.coinbase.com/v2/prices/LTC-USD/spot"set json to do shell script "sed s/warnings.*//g <<< " & jsonset value to do shell script "sed s/[a-zA-Z:{},]//g <<< " & jsonreturn "$" & value

BTTTriggers.BTTPredefinedActionName: Run Apple Script (enter directly as text)
BTTTriggers.BTTInlineAppleScript: set cvc to do shell script "curl -s 'https://bittrex.com/api/v1.1/public/getticker?market=eth-cvc' | grep -oE '(Last).*' | sed 's/[^0-9\\.]*//g'"return cvc

BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString: set json to do shell script "curl -H 'CB-VERSION: 2015-04-08' https://api.coinbase.com/v2/prices/ETH-USD/spot"set json to do shell script "sed s/warnings.*//g <<< " & jsonset eth to do shell script "sed s/[a-zA-Z:{},]//g <<< " & jsonset eth to eth as realset cvc to do shell script "curl -s 'https://bittrex.com/api/v1.1/public/getticker?market=eth-cvc' | grep -oE '(Last).*' | sed 's/[^0-9\\.]*//g'"set cvc to cvc as realset answer to cvc * ethset answer to answer * 100set answer to round answerset answer to answer / 100return "$" & answer
